channel.title: RSPS Webclient Problem!
channel.description: I just recently downloaded InsanityX source and client and I went through jar maker following each step carefully. I create the jar file and sign it. But, when i go to run the jar file it just wont open or even attempt to open. I feel as if thats the problem there. But I continue and try to add the file to my website and get a "red x error." I have the most recent java btw. Anyway I click on it and it says, "cannot execute client.class" and so I click details but that doesn't help. So I neeeeed to know how to fix this pleeeaaasee!! Thanks So much! PS I did refresh my browser and all that and I did change the server ip I have it portforwarded and I can play the desktop version only.
